Name:         Snow Leopard
Scientific:   Panthera uncia
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Mountain
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       55 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Cannot roar; uses long tail as blanket; leaps 15 meters

Name:         African Elephant
Scientific:   Loxodonta africana
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     70 years
Weight:       6000 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Largest land animal; strongest sense of smell; mourns the dead

Name:         Peregrine Falcon
Scientific:   Falco peregrinus
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Cliffs/Cities
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       1 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Fastest animal on Earth at 389 km/h in a dive

